itive-trouble</guid></item><item><title>随着肢体运动的出现，脊髓抑制细胞类型成倍增加</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/multifold-increase-in-spinal-inhibitory-cell-types-with-emergence-of-limb-movement</link><description>青蛙的变形揭示了脊髓回路如何适应新的运动需求。维贾托维奇等人。证明从基于尾部的运动向基于肢体的运动的转变与 V1 抑制性神经元的扩张和多样化相一致。跨物种比较确定了尾巴和肢体运动的保守蓝图，其中 Engrailed-1 是运动频率的全局调节器。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/multifold-increase-in-spinal-inhibitory-cell-types-with-emergence-of-limb-movement.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:12:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/multifold-increase-in-spinal-inhibitory-cell-types-with-emergence-of-limb-movement</guid></item><item><title>科学家表示，他们通过简单的鼻喷雾剂逆转了大脑衰老</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-say-theyve-reversed-brain-aging-with-a-simple-nasal-spray</link><description>德克萨斯农工大学的研究人员开发了一种鼻喷雾剂，它似乎可以通过平息炎症和恢复大脑的能量系统来逆转大脑衰老。仅服用两次剂量后，记忆和认知功能就得到了几个月的改善，这为未来针对痴呆和脑雾的治疗带来了希望。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-say-theyve-reversed-brain-aging-with-a-simple-nasal-spray.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 23:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-say-theyve-reversed-brain-aging-with-a-simple-nasal-spray</guid></item><item><title>全新天文台发现了 11,000 颗新小行星，其中包括一些掠过地球的小行星</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/11000-new-asteroids-discovered-by-a-brand-new-observatory-including-some-that-skim-close-to-earth</link><description>维拉·C·鲁宾天文台发现了 11,000 颗新小行星，其中一些距离地球非常近。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/11000-new-asteroids-discovered-by-a-brand-new-observatory-including-some-that-skim-close-to-earth.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 23:42:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/11000-new-asteroids-discovered-by-a-brand-new-observatory-including-some-that-skim-close-to-earth</guid></item></channel></rss>